{
  "stem": "5470.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said to me, uh, that he had instruction from the German commander to take these people out when they were leaving the camp.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, oh, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You are not going to take anyone out of the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you want to leave, OK, that's your business.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I am not going to keep you in here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because I didn't want to have German soldiers there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was quite a discussion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It went on until practically half past 11:00.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's where I gave in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, OK, um, you can take them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But if one hair is well, we say one hair.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If-- if there is something going to happen to these people anyhow, I keep you responsible for it, hm?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Which-- to which he agreed, and they moved out shortly after 12 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's where we got full control of the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, OK, now I'm going to give weapons to my men.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "These were all people who had carried weapons before, which were knowing how to handle weapons.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, uh, that's where we got the full control of the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that took us the whole day thereafter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't sleep a wink over the night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because the next morning, as soon as I moved out of the meeting and I gave my first instructions to the camp, what was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that circular was, uh-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] typed and multiplied.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] I came outside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I [? know ?] that one came to me, and he shook my hands with both hands.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He said, we are free!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We are free!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I said, we are not free yet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Be careful.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And, uh-- no, they were quite happy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uh, that took the whole day.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
